争，是在以毛主席为首的党中央直接领导下，在上层建筑，意识形态领域中进行一场持久的斗争──批林批孔运动正向纵深发展，势若燎原。我们是心连心的，我们都要打倒帝修反，为建设社会主义的新中国，各自在党分配的岗位上战斗着，为了表示我对同志们的祝贺，特请作家浩然同志，诗人张永枚同志，记者蒋豪济同志代表我前去看望坚持在前线的英雄们并送给你们","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"26eac33fdb","type":"paragraph","text":"──《林彪与孔孟之道》500份","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d571c7a1d","type":"paragraph","text":"──《五四以来反动派和地主资产阶级学者尊孔言论辑录》500份","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a5ea4fcde9","type":"paragraph","text":"──《批林批孔材料（一），（二）》各500份","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9035a85a46","type":"paragraph","text":"──《鲁迅批判孔孟之道言论摘录》500份","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b2ca8a3ed9","type":"paragraph","text":"学习的第一单元是毛主席《我的一点意见》，第二单元是《毛主席致江青同志的一封信》，第三单元是《毛主席视察南方时和沿途负责同志的谈话》以上三份文件请世友，紫阳同志为你们准备。中央的通知还会告诉你们其他读物。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62182abbbc","type":"paragraph","text":"致","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"32f4f1d595","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级革命的敬礼","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41f1be5ea8","type":"paragraph","text":"江青74.1.28凌晨5时","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}},"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0b2853245c","type":"paragraph","text":"──《林彪与孔孟之道》500份","index":4,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1355621fb6","type":"title","text":"江青致王洪文叶剑英张春桥邓小平陈锡联苏振华的信","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1db5c987c0","type":"pa